The protagonist, Naoya, is a first-year in high school. He asks out Saki, a girl he has been in love with, and she agrees to be his girlfriend. He's currently on cloud nine. But then, a beautiful girl named Nagisa comes up to Naoya one day and tells him that she wants to go out with him. Naoya feels himself wavering because Nagisa is such a good girl, and he comes to a decision! A new kind of romcom from a rather unexpected decision is about to begin!
(Source: Crunchyroll)
Mushoku Tensei: Isekai Ittara Honki Dasu

When a 34-year-old underachiever gets run over by a bus, his story doesn’t end there. Reincarnated in a new world as an infant, Rudeus will seize every opportunity to live the life he’s always wanted. Armed with new friends, some freshly acquired magical abilities, and the courage to do the things he’s always dreamed of, he’s embarking on an epic adventure—with all of his past experience intact!
(Source: Funimation, edited)

Tobioriru Chokuzen no Doukyuusei ni "XXX Shiyou!" to Teian Shitemita.

My first love, her name is Koga Gumomo.

She was so much more beautiful and mature than a typical high school student, which attracted a great deal of jealousy and dislike. So much so that she was on the verge of jumping off the rooftop because of all the bullying she received.

So, what can I do to help?

"Why not have s*x with me!"
"............, you pervert! ...... (yuck!)"
"Maybe so! But are you sure? If you die here, your last memory will be the confession of some pervert you don't even know! It would ruin the mood!"
"............, what have you done! You pervert!"
"I have my reasons. Because I love you more than anything in the world! Let's get married!"
"What, ehhhh~~~............?"

I will yell out my love until I die, if it will make a place for you in this world!

The most stupid and straightforward protagonist in the history of romantic comedies and the cool, sullen JK will hook up for a romantic comedy with a sugar content of 100%!

(Source: Dengeki Bunko, translated)

Love is always troubling. You want to have the courage to tell someone how you feel. You want to know who he likes. You want someone to listen to your worries. You want someone to give you a push. I know how you feel, and it hurts. Because I had a past I couldn't forget. And because now I have the "power" to save them.... That's why I, Io Akashi, became an angel. "I've finally found you, the angel of Kuze High." The angel touched the girl's cheek, in order to correct Yuzuki Minato's abnormal tendency to fall in love. This is a slightly mysterious coming-of-age story where memory and love play out softly.
(Source: Dengeki Bunko, translated)
